'''Joseph Wight''' was the cover colorist for the [[Star Wars Manga]] comic adaptations of [[Star Wars Manga: A New Hope|''A New Hope'']], [[Star Wars Manga: The Empire Strikes Back|''The Empire Strikes Back'']] and [[Star Wars Manga: Return of the Jedi|''Return of the Jedi'']].

He has also done the illustrations for a [[Star Wars]] themed "Learn to Read" book.

